// Copy to Secrets.xcconfig in this folder (Secrets.xcconfig is gitignored).
// Real Supabase URL and anon key override the placeholders in Debug.xcconfig / Release.xcconfig.
//
// NOTE: In xcconfig files, // starts a comment. Use /$()/  to escape the double-slash in URLs.
//
// SUPABASE_URL = https:/$()/YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co
// SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = (paste the anon/public key from Supabase Project Settings → API)
